  "prompt": "What is Power Testro?",
  "response": "Power Testro is a dietary supplement marketed as a testosterone booster for men. It is designed to help increase muscle mass, enhance physical performance, and improve overall energy levels. The product typically contains a blend of natural ingredients such as herbs, vitamins, and minerals that are believed to support testosterone production and male health.\n\nCommon ingredients in Power Testro may include:\n- Tribulus Terrestris\n- Fenugreek extract\n- Zinc\n- Vitamin D\n- D-Aspartic Acid\n\nIt's important to note that while some users report positive effects, the efficacy and safety of such supplements can vary. It's always recommended to consult with a healthcare provider before starting any new supplement regimen.",
